INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (15,1,'2023-10-08 10:44:36','2023-10-08 10:44:36','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">PROVIDING LEGAL SERVICES SINCE 1978</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With offices in Bethesda, Silver Spring and Washington D.C., attorney&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;provides diligent and effective legal counsel and representation to individuals and businesses. The practice includes estate and incapacity planning, estate administration, also known as probate, business and commercial transactions, commercial real estate transactions, and contract counsel, negotiating and drafting.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you hire this law firm, you will work directly with&nbsp;Susan Eleff, a highly-trained lawyer with more than 40 years of solid hands-on experience. Susans entire legal team provides legal services that are both personal and professional, and the firms success is evident in its client endorsements and peer reviews. Ms. Eleff holds an AV Preeminent* peer-review rating through Martindale-Hubbell, the services highest rating, and a 10.0 Superb rating from the Avvo attorney rating service, that services highest score.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2023-10-08 10:44:36','2023-10-08 10:44:36','',10,'http://elefflaw.local/?p=15',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (16,1,'2023-10-08 15:34:57','2023-10-08 15:34:57','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">COST-EFFECTIVE, RESULTS-ORIENTED LEGAL SERVICES FOR BUSINESSES</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In her 40 years of practicing law, attorney&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;has gained a reputation among business owners and peers for her efficient, cost-effective and results-oriented legal services. Today, she offers comprehensive business transaction, document drafting, negotiation and consulting from her Maryland offices in Bethesda and Silver Spring, in addition to her Washington D.C. location.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a small-business owner herself, Ms. Eleff respects that business owners need to look out for the bottom line in all transactions. She is careful and proficient in not wasting time and money on legal services that arent needed by her clients. She tailors her recommendations for those that are needed, and those that will produce the most efficient and cost-effective results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Susan Eleff&nbsp;is an experienced and deal-oriented business attorney who can help you form a startup business, buy or sell a business, draft or review contracts enter into financing, employment and contractor arrangements and negotiate and document virtually any business transaction that a small or medium-sized business may encounter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Legal Services For Businesses</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Entrepreneurs and business owners face a host of legal issues from the day they launch their concept or open their doors. When you work with our legal team at&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group, you can focus the daily operations of your business knowing that your companys legal matters are in good hands.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Susan Eleff&nbsp;holds an *AV Preeminent* peer-review rating through Martindale-Hubbell, the services highest rating, and a 10.0 Superb rating from the Avvo rating agency.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;provides the following legal services to businesses in Montgomery County, Prince Georges County and throughout northern Virginia:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/business-transactions/business-formation/\">Business formation of startups and subsidiaries</a>, including sole proprietorships, partnership startups, limited liability companies (LLCs) and corporate startups</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Buy-sell agreements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Transfer of ownership</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Employment and consulting contracts, including stock options and other incentive compensation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Independent contractor agreements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Commercial contracts</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Financing agreements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Leases and other landlord-tenant agreements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/business-transactions/business-succession-planning/\">Business succession planning</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Business dissolution</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When it comes to protecting your business interests and closing a deal, it is critical you have a lawyer you can trust.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Discuss Your Business Needs</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more information about&nbsp;The Eleff Law Groups business services, or to discuss your business need in detail, please call&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+1-800-765-2662\">800-765-2662</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/contact/\">schedule a legal consultation online</a>. Initial consultations of up to 15 minutes are complimentary and confidential. Certain limitations may apply.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>AV Preeminent and BV Distinguished are certification marks of Reed Elsevier Properties Inc., used in accordance with the Martindale-Hubbell certification procedures, standards and policies. Martindale-Hubbell is the facilitator of a peer review rating process. Ratings reflect the confidential opinions of members of the Bar and the judiciary. Martindale-Hubbell ratings fall into two categories  legal ability and general ethical standards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Business Transactions','','publish','closed','closed','','business-transactions','','','2023-10-08 19:13:09','2023-10-08 19:13:09','',0,'http://elefflaw.local/?page_id=16',0,'page','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (17,1,'2023-10-08 15:34:57','2023-10-08 15:34:57','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">COST-EFFECTIVE, RESULTS-ORIENTED LEGAL SERVICES FOR BUSINESSES</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In her 40 years of practicing law, attorney&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;has gained a reputation among business owners and peers for her efficient, cost-effective and results-oriented legal services. Today, she offers comprehensive business transaction, document drafting, negotiation and consulting from her Maryland offices in Bethesda and Silver Spring, in addition to her Washington D.C. location.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a small-business owner herself, Ms. Eleff respects that business owners need to look out for the bottom line in all transactions. She is careful and proficient in not wasting time and money on legal services that arent needed by her clients. She tailors her recommendations for those that are needed, and those that will produce the most efficient and cost-effective results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Susan Eleff&nbsp;is an experienced and deal-oriented business attorney who can help you form a startup business, buy or sell a business, draft or review contracts enter into financing, employment and contractor arrangements and negotiate and document virtually any business transaction that a small or medium-sized business may encounter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Business Transactions','','inherit','closed','closed','','16-revision-v1','','','2023-10-08 15:34:57','2023-10-08 15:34:57','',16,'http://elefflaw.local/?p=17',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (18,1,'2023-10-08 15:35:41','2023-10-08 15:35:41','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FORMING A NEW BUSINESS</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With offices in Bethesda, Silver Spring, Maryland, and Washington, D.C.,&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;of&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;represents entrepreneurs during the business formation process. Ms.Eleff, the firms experienced and accomplished founder, understands the legal challenges that new businesses and business owners face. As your lawyer, she will help you develop a detailed and strategic legal strategy that sets your venture up for success.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Susan Eleff&nbsp;is *AV Preeminent peer-review rated through Martindale-Hubbell. This is the services highest rating.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are starting a new company or expanding an existing business, one of the first steps is to enlist a knowledgeable business formation attorney like&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;and her team to help you select the most suitable legal structure.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Counseling New Businesses On Choice of Entity</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are starting a new company or expanding an existing business, you can benefit from working with a knowledgeable business formation attorney like&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;to select the most suitable legal structure. The ideal entity selection depends on your business objectives, among other factors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Different business forms have varying tax and liability consequences.&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;and her team can counsel you on which entity to choose as well as prepare and file the necessary documentation to properly organize your business under Maryland law. Common entities include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Sole proprietorships</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Partnerships</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Limited partnerships</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Limited liability companies (LLCs)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Corporations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After selecting the most appropriate entity,&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;can assist you in properly setting up your business by drafting partnership agreements, operating agreements, articles of incorporation or organization, employment contracts and more.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Acquiring Commercial Property</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;is also experienced in commercial real estate. If you are considering&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/commercial-real-estate/\">buying or leasing commercial property</a>&nbsp;for your business venture, the firm can navigate you through the process.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As your commercial real estate attorney,&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;and her team will offer experienced representation offering a tailored suite of legal services to help you accomplish your goals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Set Up Your Company The Right Way. Contact&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;for Help.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To discuss your business formation concerns call&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+1-800-765-2662\">800-765-2662</a>&nbsp;or schedule a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/contact/\">free initial consultation online</a>. Certain limitations may apply. The firm handles cases throughout Montgomery County, Prince Georges County and throughout northern Virginia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>AV Preeminent and BV Distinguished are certification marks of Reed Elsevier Properties Inc., used in accordance with the Martindale-Hubbell certification procedures, standards and policies. Martindale-Hubbell is the facilitator of a peer review rating process. Ratings reflect the confidential opinions of members of the Bar and the judiciary. Martindale-Hubbell ratings fall into two categories  legal ability and general ethical standards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Business Formation','','publish','closed','closed','','business-formation','','','2023-10-08 19:13:27','2023-10-08 19:13:27','',16,'http://elefflaw.local/?page_id=18',0,'page','',0);
