INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (52,1,'2023-10-08 19:14:26','2023-10-08 19:14:26','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">TRUSTED GUIDANCE AND COUNSEL DURING COMMERCIAL REAL ESTATE TRANSACTIONS</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Commercial real estate is a significant and complicated investment, whether you are a property owner or a small-business proprietor looking to lease a space.&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;provides comprehensive commercial real estate services designed to protect your interests. The firm has Maryland offices in Bethesda and Silver Spring, as well as Washington D.C. to meet your needs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Susan Eleff&nbsp;is an experienced lawyer with more than 40 years of legal experience handling commercial real estate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/business-transactions/\">matters for business owners</a>, property owners, investors and other interested parties. She and her team are well-qualified to provide counsel, document drafting services and negotiation regarding a variety of real estate matters, including:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Property acquisitions, purchase agreements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Lease and other landlord-tenant agreements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Development agreements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Financial transactions</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Dealings with banks and lenders, including workouts, refinancing and foreclosure prevention</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tax-free exchanges</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Restrictive covenants</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Easements</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Clearing titles</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether the client is a private or public company, an institutional investor or a developer, hiring a skilled and strategic commercial real estate attorney with&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;will simplify and expedite a variety of commercial transactions and dealings.&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;and her team have handled straightforward transactions as well as complex projects involving multifaceted financing deals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Practical And Cost-Effective Legal Counsel</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Susan Eleff&nbsp;has more than 35 years of experience and an excellent record of results. Her success is attributed to her commitment to providing high-quality services customized to each clients unique needs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whatever your need,&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;can provide coordinated, tailored legal services for transactions of nearly any type or size in Montgomery County, Prince Georges County and throughout northern Virginia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Schedule A Complimentary Initial Consultation With&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Call&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+1-800-765-2662\">800-765-2662</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/contact/\">fill out this form</a>&nbsp;to schedule a commercial real estate consultation with&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group. Your initial consultation will be provided free of charge*.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>*Certain limitations may apply to our free consultation offer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Commercial Real Estate','','inherit','closed','closed','','29-revision-v1','','','2023-10-08 19:14:26','2023-10-08 19:14:26','',29,'http://elefflaw.local/?p=52',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (53,1,'2023-10-08 19:14:46','2023-10-08 19:14:46','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">PROTECTING YOUR FINANCIAL AND PROPERTY INTERESTS THROUGH A PRENUPTIAL AGREEMENT</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A marriage is not only a relationship. It is a legal partnership. While your relationship may be governed by you and your partner, your legal partnership is governed by the state of Maryland. Many engaged couples want to take over the legal control of their marriage, and they do this by entering into prenuptial relationships.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Deciding to draft and sign a prenuptial agreement does not mean you are expecting your marriage to fail. It means you want to stipulate the terms and conditions of your legal financial partnership.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prenuptial agreements are important tools for those who are bringing substantial assets into marriage, those who are getting married for the second or third time, and those with children from previous relationships. When one fianc has a large income, a significant debt load or is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/probate/\">expecting an inheritance</a>, it is also wise to consider creating a prenuptial agreement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With offices in Bethesda, Silver Spring and Washington, D.C., our attorney at&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group, drafts and negotiates prenuptial agreements for clients throughout the region. With more than 40 years of legal experience,&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;has the proven knowledge and skill to protect your legal rights and interests as you prepare for marriage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Is In Your Prenuptial Agreement?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not all prenuptial agreements are alike.&nbsp;Susan Eleff&nbsp;and her team will work with you to determine your needs and interests before drafting agreements that are beneficial to you. As your lawyer, Ms. Eleff will take the time to listen to your concerns, and deliver efficient and effective legal guidance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your prenuptial agreement may address any of the following issues, among others:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Property division</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Spousal support</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Conditions of guardianship</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Terms of forfeiture</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Rules of divorce</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/estate-planning-and-probate/\">Estate planning, wills and trusts</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Learn More About Prenuptial Agreements</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To discuss your concerns or needs regarding prenuptial agreements with&nbsp;The Eleff Law Group&nbsp;call&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+1-800-765-2662\">800-765-2662</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.elefflaw.com/contact/\">complete this form</a>&nbsp;to schedule a legal consultation. Your initial legal consultation will be provided free of charge (certain limitations apply), and the contents of your conversation will be confidential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Prenuptial Agreements','','inherit','closed','closed','','33-revision-v1','','','2023-10-08 19:14:46','2023-10-08 19:14:46','',33,'http://elefflaw.local/?p=53',0,'revision','',0);
